# Transient cross-build artifacts of the thirdparty-bldtool.
# The built prefix (native/prefix/) IS committed (it is the reusable build
# input for crengine-ng / Phase 1b), but the unpacked upstream sources and
# per-package state caches are not — they are re-fetchable via build.sh.
thirdparty/thirdparty-bldtool/sources/
thirdparty/thirdparty-bldtool/tmp/
thirdparty/thirdparty-bldtool/*.log

# Per-package build dirs (created next to sources/).
thirdparty/thirdparty-bldtool/*-build-*/
